Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CityMap
    CityMap class, represents the map of a city Contains a list and a map of nodes, and a list of sections
    Delivery
    Delivery class, a delivery is represented by an id, a client, the address of a node.
    DeliveryRound
    DeliveryRound class Represents a delivery round, with a list of paths, a start hour, an end hour and a duration
    Node
    Node class, identified by an id, and two coordinates.
    Path
    Path class Represents a path between two deliveries points (departure & arrival).
    Section
    Section class A section is determined by a street name, the departure node, the arrival node, the speed and the length
    TimeWindow
    TimeWindow class A time window is determined by a starting hour, an ending hour, and a list of deliveries
    TypicalDay
    TypicalDay class A typical day is basically a working day, it contains several time window launched from a warehouse It also contains the list of planned deliveries
